<h1>Dataset Description</h1>

<p>
  This project uses a large books dataset containing over 58,000 books and
  related information about authors, publishers, languages, and ratings.
</p>

<p>
  The data was imported from a CSV file into a Ruby on Rails database using
  a custom seed script. The application allows users to browse, search, and
  filter the imported data.
</p>

<h2>Dataset Fields</h2>

<ul>
  <li>Book title</li>
  <li>Author</li>
  <li>Publisher</li>
  <li>Category</li>
  <li>Language</li>
  <li>ISBN</li>
  <li>Average Rating</li>
  <li>Number of Pages</li>
</ul>